      "text": "芽衣が結婚するなら、家にいても、出かけても\nずっと楽しく一緒にいられる人がいいな",
      "startTime": 149.5000017803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.8666736127
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば……芽衣、{user}さんと\nいると、どこで何してても楽しいよ！",
      "startTime": 156.4429127085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "え。芽衣？　それって……",
      "startTime": 160.1333402794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.9333402794
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "あとはねー、月ストのみんなでしょ？\nそれから家族もそうだし、猫ちゃんも！",
      "startTime": 167.4000017803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そういうことか……びっくりした",
      "startTime": 171.0666736127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.800006946
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.0333351136
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "あ、準備出来たみたいだよ！\nまずは芽衣一人で撮るみたい。見ててねー！",
      "startTime": 178.0333351136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
